{"tid":1975601,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"母愛真係好偉大","createTime":"2020-04-16T15:54:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T16:22:39.000Z","uid":203454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c51c082e5ac0ba405fbb253687b178995b83ae92","tid":1975601,"uid":203454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:54:52.000Z","msg":"有媽媽喺身邊真係好幸福<br />\n成日驚自己會學壞<br />\n唔俾我上網打機<br />\n閂埋門都會強行爆開我房門<br />\n就算係深夜都會特登起身睇下我做緊咩<br />\n一諗起就眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712d0bfaebe05836ed8c8d8274fe88c1dfaf088f","tid":1975601,"uid":132174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:57:16.000Z","msg":"沉醉於lol她不讚賞~"},{"pid":"42671c290ae56d331c432b1ad5e589688067735e","tid":1975601,"uid":106633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:59:46.000Z","msg":"潮文已經提示咗你要點做<br />\n<br />\n話說頭先我打緊LoL個陣<br />\n我老母無端端捧碗湯入黎話今日天氣凍 叫我飲左佢暖吓個身 唔好凍病<br />\n咁打緊LoL又點分神飲湯 咁咪話一陣飲<br />\n點知我老母5分鐘入黎煩我一次<br />\n最後我頂唔撚順係佢面前倒晒佢碗湯落地下<br />\n跟住佢眼濕濕扮委屈咁拖返乾撻地 我心諗你一開始唔好咁煩咪得囉 你逼我飲我就係都唔飲呀你吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9dc39d2d0ba1eef4c8c8f7c42b6b867cb98a7e4","tid":1975601,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"衰仔包咁你記得孝順老母喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b458bbae82b59d787406cdae520c98a57a407d78","tid":1975601,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:06:31.000Z","msg":"仲會係你打緊lol嗰陣gank你"},{"pid":"88c9a7170ed0442bb711de563758b5bb8f9b0c53","tid":1975601,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T16:06:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/